This is the second version of the Col Cristobal Colon map located in San Bernardino Py, it is not finished and it lacks many corrections, but I think it is playable, it does not have props, it does not have lights or details because the computer could not finish the compilation although I would have liked to include them and the windows are poorly designed, because bots cannot use them well. I took some liberties with the design and the sizes, for example the windows are very large, to facilitate the passage through them it does not have custom textures because I was kaigue (lazy) to go to take photos and I do not think it was worth it either

This is the first map I make, during its development I learned how to use the hammer tool.

Don't expect much from him
anyways... thanks in advance
